          "id": 4553,
          "question": "What should schools, child care and summer programs in Vermont do?",
          "answer": "\n\nSchools will reopen in the fall for in-person instruction. The Agency of Education and the Health Department created a guidance document for school administrators and personnel as they plan and implement the reopening of schools for the 2020-21 school year. Read [A Strong and Healthy Start: Safety and Health Guidance for Reopening Schools, Fall 2020](https://education.vermont.gov/documents/guidance-strong-healthy-start-health-guidance). Find more [COVID-19 guidance for Vermont schools](https://education.vermont.gov/news/covid-19-guidance-vermont-schools) from the Agency of Education.\n\nChild care providers can decide to reopen if they follow health and safety precautions. Some may choose not to reopen or are unable to do so. Find [guidance on child care](https://accd.vermont.gov/content/stay-home-stay-safe-sector-specific-guidance#education-childcare) from the Agency of Commerce and Community Development as it becomes available.\n\n**Guidance and Resources for Child Care and Summer Programs**\n\n*   [Health Guidance for Childcare and School Age Camps/Care](https://www.healthvermont.gov/sites/default/files/documents/pdf/COVID19-Health-Guidance-Childcare-Summer-Programs.pdf) that are or will open during the COVID-19 pandemic\n*   [Health & Safety Guidance for Childcare & Summer Programs FAQ](https://www.healthvermont.gov/sites/default/files/documents/pdf/COVID-Childcare-Summer-Program-Guidance-FAQ.pdf)\n*   [Sample Daily COVID-19 Health Checklist Child Care and School Age Camps/Care](https://www.healthvermont.gov/sites/default/files/documents/pdf/COVID19-Childcare-Camp-Daily-Health-Checklist-Template.pdf)\n*   [Sample Weekly COVID-19 Health Checklist Child Care and School Age Camps/Care](https://www.healthvermont.gov/sites/default/files/documents/pdf/COVID19-Childcare-Camp-Weekly-Health-Checklist-Template.pdf)\n\nFind more [resources and information for schools, child care and summer programs](https://www.healthvermont.gov/COVID19-schools).",
