          "question": "Do I need to quarantine if someone I had close contact with is under quarantine?",
          "answer": "\n\nNo. You do not need to quarantine if you had close contact with someone who is under quarantine. \n\nIf you are living with someone who is under quarantine, stay at least 6 feet from them. People under quarantine should wear a mask in common spaces. Be sure to disinfect commonly touched surfaces, and check yourself for symptoms for 14 days.",
